      "date": "2011-07-15 09:24:11.000000000",
      "message": "Patch Set 3:\n\nI just found s_mb_prealloc_table was introduced by patch ext4-prealloc-rhel6.patch. Since ext4_mb_init_backend() was called after the memory allocation for sbi->s_mb_prealloc_table, \"kfree(sbi->s_mb_prealloc_table)\" should be called if ext4_mb_init_backend() failed. This is the difference between patch set 3 and 2.",
